The Spar Group Says Fiscal First-Half Profit Increases to $71.1 Million

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-05-11T05:08:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-11/the-spar-group-says-fiscal-first-half-profit-increases-to-71-1-million.html
The  Spar Group Ltd. (SPP)  said fiscal
first-half net income rose to 479.2 million rand from 474.9
million rand a year earlier.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
